			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left Analog Stick</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Jump:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Duck:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Attack / Tail swipe attack while jumping / Throw small objects you picked up / Activate switches:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pick up small objects / Move large objects while holding button and using direction / Hold after jumping to glide:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Move camera:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 or R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Display or hide onscreen information:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Turn on/off vibration:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game / Brings up in game menu/Skips FMVs and hints:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br><br>
